Class AbstractGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.voxelgameslib.voxelgameslib.game.AbstractGame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Game, Tickable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomGame, EditModeGame

    public abstract class AbstractGame
extends java.lang.Object
implements Game
    Abstract implementation of a Game. Handles broadcasting, ticking and user management.
